WEBVTT

00:06.499 --> 00:07.840
(Respect copyright)

00:14.112 --> 00:20.704
ظآزMemories hold you back
from fulfilling your dreamsظآز

00:24.288 --> 00:30.432
ظآزOnly by moving forward
can you find reunionظآز

00:32.640 --> 00:35.872
ظآزEndings only mark new routesظآز

00:36.096 --> 00:42.112
ظآزIt's all part of the sceneryظآز

00:42.432 --> 00:45.856
ظآزTo the horizon's callظآز

00:45.920 --> 00:52.480
ظآزYour journey hasn't startedظآز

00:53.536 --> 00:57.472
ظآزTowards mountains,
chase the stars brightظآز

00:57.472 --> 01:03.552
ظآزLet time embrace you
and wash away the pastظآز

01:03.840 --> 01:07.712
ظآزPut every twist behind youظآز

01:07.712 --> 01:12.576
ظآزDrift leisurely through timeظآز

01:12.960 --> 01:15.680
ظآزMake headway against the windظآز

01:15.680 --> 01:18.667
ظآزLet mountains bow to your paceظآز

01:18.720 --> 01:24.128
ظآزRush towards a life without regretظآز

01:24.640 --> 01:28.579
ظآزLet your nature burst freeظآز

01:30.240 --> 01:34.490
=The First Jasmine=

01:35.344 --> 01:37.808
=Episode 18=

01:38.660 --> 01:39.581
You eat your soup.

01:39.581 --> 01:40.701
You may go.

01:41.981 --> 01:42.941
You have to rewrite.

01:44.900 --> 01:46.020
Let me check.

01:49.300 --> 01:50.540
Luckily, the inside isn't wet.

01:51.781 --> 01:53.221
You go take a seat.

01:53.820 --> 01:54.861
Leave it alone.

01:56.820 --> 01:57.820
You eat your soup.

02:13.540 --> 02:14.501
Is Qingshuang here?

02:14.901 --> 02:16.021
Why?

02:16.660 --> 02:17.501
I'll call her over.

02:17.781 --> 02:18.461
No need.

02:21.540 --> 02:22.901
What plans do you have today?

02:23.700 --> 02:26.021
After writing the letter,
I need to go to Shende Shop.

02:26.660 --> 02:27.700
I'll go with you.

02:28.501 --> 02:29.781
You have the day off again?

02:30.221 --> 02:31.536
I'll go to work in the afternoon.

02:32.260 --> 02:33.941
I haven't even been to your shop.

02:34.380 --> 02:36.781
It's also my business, after all.
I should go take a look.

02:37.901 --> 02:39.260
Your business?

02:39.621 --> 02:41.621
That was my dowry from my mom.

02:42.781 --> 02:44.181
I even gave you all my property.

02:44.820 --> 02:46.260
But I haven't given you mine.

02:48.380 --> 02:49.901
That's rather stingy of you.

02:55.380 --> 02:56.181
Alright.

02:57.820 --> 02:59.380
Even though it's your private asset,

02:59.660 --> 03:01.621
it shouldn't hurt to take a look, right?

03:04.501 --> 03:05.941
I'll have Jin mail them for you.

03:06.260 --> 03:08.380
No need. Qingshuang will handle it.

03:09.540 --> 03:10.941
Qingshuang is quite capable.

03:11.540 --> 03:13.860
At least, she is better
than some troublemaker.

03:20.260 --> 03:22.540
Alright, shall we go
to my shop right now?

03:30.461 --> 03:31.140
I need your help.

03:34.181 --> 03:36.061
Your Highness,
you've gained some weight.

03:36.260 --> 03:37.621
The food must have been delicious.

03:38.181 --> 03:40.021
Perhaps you need to get more exercise.

03:41.941 --> 03:42.741
Hey, please.

03:43.781 --> 03:44.580
Are you afraid?

03:44.781 --> 03:46.061
I'm afraid you might fall.

03:46.580 --> 03:47.741
If you are, I'll slow down.

03:50.140 --> 03:51.820
Look, he's convulsing.

03:51.980 --> 03:53.461
Was he hit by something?

03:53.660 --> 03:55.221
- His mouth is purplish!
- Wake up!

03:55.741 --> 03:57.221
Whose employee is this?

03:57.221 --> 03:58.341
What should we do?

03:58.341 --> 03:59.181
Just moments ago...

03:59.181 --> 04:01.301
A fallen crate hit him in the chest.

04:01.901 --> 04:02.860
Take a look!

04:03.021 --> 04:05.461
His chest is puffed up
like an inflatable bag.

04:07.660 --> 04:08.621
Inflatable bag?

04:10.341 --> 04:12.260
Sir, what should we do?

04:12.380 --> 04:13.540
Is there a physician?

04:14.221 --> 04:15.021
Please step aside.

04:23.184 --> 04:24.272
How did this happen?

04:26.288 --> 04:27.504
Get him to a clinic.

04:30.181 --> 04:32.380
Purple face, breathing fast,
and bulging neck veins.

04:33.220 --> 04:36.020
The fallen crate
crushed his internal organs.

04:36.621 --> 04:38.621
His lung is damaged.
He is in danger now.

04:39.020 --> 04:40.181
Tear open his robe.

04:40.621 --> 04:42.981
Young Lady, how could you
unlace a man's robe on the street?

04:43.220 --> 04:43.900
Exactly!

04:43.900 --> 04:45.101
People are watching.

04:45.101 --> 04:46.260
Quite inappropriate.

04:46.260 --> 04:47.580
Watch your manners!

04:47.580 --> 04:48.380
Hurry!

04:58.580 --> 04:59.460
Press on his ribs!

04:59.632 --> 05:00.528
A knife?

05:01.616 --> 05:02.576
Will this work?

05:02.640 --> 05:03.504
Stabbing him?

05:05.008 --> 05:06.096
He's already in danger.

05:14.501 --> 05:16.101
I've let the air out of his lungs.

05:16.501 --> 05:17.741
He needs to lie flat.

05:18.301 --> 05:19.981
Get him to a clinic quickly.

05:20.220 --> 05:22.421
Otherwise, nobody can save him!

05:24.336 --> 05:26.020
(Shende Shop)

05:26.020 --> 05:26.820
Careful.

05:33.820 --> 05:35.460
They became inseparable.

05:51.101 --> 05:53.220
The accounts are complex.
Can you make sense of them?

05:55.741 --> 05:59.700
Your Highness, do you know
who wrote "Essentials of Mathematics"?

06:01.780 --> 06:03.020
One of your tutors?

06:04.501 --> 06:06.741
Master Chen of Lishan Academy.

06:08.140 --> 06:10.340
Your tutor wrote it, not you!

06:10.340 --> 06:12.421
So, can you read the ledger?

06:13.900 --> 06:15.820
Princess Ding is remarkably intelligent.

06:16.340 --> 06:17.941
Back in the Lishan Academy,

06:18.501 --> 06:19.900
our tutor often said

06:20.820 --> 06:22.780
that Princess Ding was young

06:23.140 --> 06:26.741
but better at accounting
and calculations

06:26.741 --> 06:29.621
than all his senior disciples.

06:30.020 --> 06:31.700
No need to praise me.

06:31.981 --> 06:33.900
You manage so many shops

06:34.101 --> 06:36.301
and take care of many things.
You've worked so hard.

06:36.380 --> 06:37.700
You deserve praise.

06:37.700 --> 06:38.900
You flatter me.

06:39.020 --> 06:40.421
But to be honest,

06:40.501 --> 06:44.700
I'm getting increasingly busy.

06:45.220 --> 06:47.460
I can't handle it alone anymore.

06:47.700 --> 06:50.941
I think it's time to hire some workers.

06:51.181 --> 06:52.700
You decide.

06:53.900 --> 06:56.220
You may go do your things.
No need to stay here.

06:59.460 --> 07:00.421
I'm leaving.

07:01.741 --> 07:05.700
Oh, this is the book you requested.

07:05.820 --> 07:06.780
Thank you.

07:10.981 --> 07:13.580
Any plans after finishing the ledger?

07:15.941 --> 07:16.981
Nothing else.

07:17.700 --> 07:20.541
Come with me
to the prefecture office then.

07:21.981 --> 07:24.421
You're on duty there. Why should I go?

07:24.501 --> 07:25.301
To accompany me.

07:27.140 --> 07:30.020
I refuse. Jingzhao Prefecture is stuffy.

07:31.421 --> 07:33.301
But I came to the shop with you.

07:35.061 --> 07:36.460
I didn't ask you to come.

07:37.181 --> 07:38.541
You came of your own accord.

07:39.181 --> 07:39.981
You...

07:40.301 --> 07:41.140
Master Feng.

07:41.900 --> 07:42.780
Zhuang.

07:43.700 --> 07:44.460
Please come inside.

07:49.421 --> 07:50.501
Greetings, Your Highness.

07:55.301 --> 07:57.820
Your Highness, you didn't
stop by the Qingfeng Mingyue Tower.

07:57.861 --> 07:58.900
Why is that?

07:59.020 --> 08:02.061
Well, I came to my own shop.

08:02.181 --> 08:03.301
Must I report to you?

08:04.421 --> 08:05.541
Your own shop, huh?

08:06.020 --> 08:07.780
Jinbao Shop has been open for six years.

08:08.380 --> 08:10.340
Yet His Highness has never been there.

08:12.580 --> 08:13.941
Times have changed.

08:15.020 --> 08:18.340
Your Highness,
I advise you to be careful.

08:20.900 --> 08:24.340
One moment, someone holds you dear.

08:24.501 --> 08:26.380
The next, they change as they please.

08:26.700 --> 08:30.541
When they favor you,
they praise your genius in trade.

08:30.820 --> 08:32.860
They long to entrust everything to you.

08:32.980 --> 08:34.141
When you lose favor,

08:34.460 --> 08:38.460
they turn their backs on you
and offer it all to others.

08:39.181 --> 08:40.740
I'm so unlucky.

08:41.820 --> 08:43.141
Your Highness, take a look.

08:44.580 --> 08:45.781
What do I hold in my hands?

08:47.860 --> 08:48.980
Nothing at all.

08:49.700 --> 08:52.381
Yes! Completely empty.

08:53.220 --> 08:56.820
So, you must be careful.

08:58.340 --> 08:59.261
Are you done?

08:59.460 --> 09:00.980
Let's go. Time to work.

09:02.061 --> 09:02.860
Okay.

09:03.261 --> 09:05.061
We haven't met for several days.

09:05.220 --> 09:06.421
Let's chat more.

09:08.901 --> 09:12.941
Your Highness,
come to your own shop again.

09:22.021 --> 09:23.901
Your medical skills are impressive.

09:23.901 --> 09:25.820
Thank you for saving the patient.

09:26.460 --> 09:27.860
You two have blood stains.

09:27.860 --> 09:31.021
If you don't mind,
follow me inside for a quick cleaning.

09:32.781 --> 09:33.580
Alright.

10:08.980 --> 10:10.941
Your knife has an unusual form.

10:11.740 --> 10:13.781
Looks like the triangular knives
in the southwest.

10:14.340 --> 10:15.460
Good eye, sir.

10:16.620 --> 10:18.661
Earlier, you seemed calm and composed.

10:19.620 --> 10:20.620
Do you know medicine?

10:21.820 --> 10:22.860
Late autumn last year,

10:23.340 --> 10:25.661
I stayed in a southwestern hamlet
for a month or so.

10:25.860 --> 10:27.661
I learned some methods
from their physician.

10:27.980 --> 10:30.820
So I learned about pneumothorax.

10:30.820 --> 10:32.580
It's not a life-threatening illness.

10:32.901 --> 10:34.820
If the air trapped in the chest
can't get out,

10:35.100 --> 10:36.460
it will suffocate a person alive.

10:40.421 --> 10:42.460
Is the hamlet near the Chishui Valley?

10:43.700 --> 10:46.141
Yes! How do you know?

10:46.740 --> 10:49.261
That place is remote
and sparsely populated.

10:50.100 --> 10:50.980
You've been there?

10:52.820 --> 10:53.620
On business.

10:53.980 --> 10:54.941
When?

10:56.061 --> 10:56.980
Early this spring.

10:58.500 --> 10:59.820
How coincidental.

11:00.021 --> 11:02.021
I just left, and then you arrived.

11:03.141 --> 11:05.980
Did you pass the Qianxing Inn
outside the valley?

11:06.421 --> 11:09.740
Their snake gall liquor
is strong and spicy.

11:09.941 --> 11:12.141
I've been craving that liquor
since leaving.

11:13.620 --> 11:14.580
I stayed two days.

11:15.301 --> 11:17.580
Just as the owner had a baby,

11:17.820 --> 11:20.061
their snake gall liquor is half price.

11:41.181 --> 11:41.980
Are you okay?

11:42.980 --> 11:46.421
When I was there last year,
she hadn't delivered yet.

11:46.421 --> 11:47.381
She had a big belly.

11:48.620 --> 11:49.820
Tell me!

11:50.421 --> 11:52.021
Were the mother and child safe?

11:52.021 --> 11:53.421
Did she have a boy or a girl?

11:53.421 --> 11:54.460
What was the weight?

11:56.141 --> 11:58.181
Both were safe. A baby girl.

12:00.620 --> 12:01.421
You two.

12:03.061 --> 12:04.500
The patient is now out of danger.

12:04.500 --> 12:06.460
His wife came here to care for him.

12:06.460 --> 12:09.021
But his family is poor,
growing melons for a living.

12:09.100 --> 12:11.181
They can't afford to pay you.

12:11.421 --> 12:13.421
His wife is grateful for your kindness.

12:13.421 --> 12:16.460
She brought two homegrown melons
for you two.

12:19.301 --> 12:21.061
Money isn't better than melon!

12:21.872 --> 12:23.216
I'm glad you like it.

12:35.580 --> 12:36.381
Have a try.

12:40.340 --> 12:41.381
But your knife?

12:42.421 --> 12:44.421
I've wiped it. It's clean.

12:51.460 --> 12:53.860
Back in the southwest,
I stumbled into wolves.

12:53.860 --> 12:56.261
I used this very knife
to kill the wolf pack.

12:58.700 --> 13:01.620
And then I still slice meat with it.

13:02.141 --> 13:04.500
People say
unhygienic food makes them sick.

13:04.500 --> 13:05.740
That's nonsense.

13:05.941 --> 13:08.820
The sturdier people become,
the better their lives are.

13:14.261 --> 13:16.820
Turns out a melon cut with your knife
tastes this sweet.

13:17.740 --> 13:18.980
I told you it was sweet!

13:19.952 --> 13:25.424
(Ren'an Clinic)

13:26.941 --> 13:28.021
It's getting late.

13:32.100 --> 13:32.901
Indeed.

13:35.941 --> 13:38.661
I'm leaving.

14:06.381 --> 14:09.296
Don't move or speak.

14:13.860 --> 14:15.541
Since you've been to the Chishui Valley,

14:16.261 --> 14:19.181
you must know
there's an unwritten custom there.

14:19.740 --> 14:22.460
Love at first sight is tested
by a three-day pact.

14:23.181 --> 14:25.616
If you don't get over me
after three days,

14:26.541 --> 14:28.460
come find me at this address.

14:30.781 --> 14:32.100
We met by chance.

14:33.541 --> 14:36.781
I don't even know your name.

14:37.220 --> 14:38.541
I'm Lin Tinglan.

14:38.781 --> 14:41.181
T I N G, L A N.

14:42.100 --> 14:45.872
As for your name,
tell me next time we meet.

15:02.512 --> 15:06.352
(Lakeview Garden)

15:06.480 --> 15:08.816
(Jingzhao Prefecture)

15:09.008 --> 15:10.160
(The Legend of Gallant Knights)
(Tales of Distant Mountains)

15:11.261 --> 15:12.860
You've read them?

15:13.860 --> 15:15.460
The Legend of Gallant Knights,

15:15.661 --> 15:17.021
Tales of Distant Mountains.

15:17.860 --> 15:20.901
I never read romance stories.

15:21.500 --> 15:22.781
Luckily, I brought my books.

15:25.500 --> 15:26.980
Let me see what you've brought.

15:33.141 --> 15:34.740
Notes on the Armillary Sphere,

15:37.381 --> 15:38.860
Commentary on the Taichu Calendar.

15:38.860 --> 15:39.860
You even know this stuff?

15:41.381 --> 15:42.941
I only know a little.

15:45.181 --> 15:47.500
The sun, moon, and stars
follow constant rules,

15:47.700 --> 15:49.021
moving along their natural paths.

15:50.021 --> 15:52.021
For example,
the Seven-Star Alignment is considered

15:52.261 --> 15:53.580
a once-in-a-century event,

15:53.860 --> 15:56.301
but it's just down
to varying orbital cycles,

15:56.381 --> 15:59.141
with unfixed intersection intervals.

15:59.141 --> 16:00.580
Many factors influence this.

16:01.941 --> 16:04.261
The celestial events
like Mars lingering near Antares,

16:04.340 --> 16:06.781
Venus crossing the sky,
and the moon eclipsing the Pleiades,

16:07.261 --> 16:10.261
all can be precisely calculated

16:10.261 --> 16:13.301
to find their best viewing times
and locations.

16:14.740 --> 16:15.541
That's impressive.

16:19.261 --> 16:20.261
Then keep reading.

16:20.460 --> 16:22.100
I'll review official documents.

16:39.941 --> 16:41.740
Your Highness, enjoy your tea.

17:01.460 --> 17:02.261
Are you all right?

17:04.861 --> 17:06.740
I've calculated an intriguing event.

17:06.740 --> 17:08.621
It would happen soon.

17:09.300 --> 17:10.300
Very soon?

17:12.101 --> 17:14.700
Pinpointing it exactly proves tricky.

17:18.740 --> 17:19.780
Do you need my help?

17:21.740 --> 17:22.540
No need.

17:22.740 --> 17:23.581
Are you sure?

17:29.901 --> 17:31.141
You think I can't help, right?

17:36.336 --> 17:39.632
ظآزFortunately, the wounds
the world gave meظآز

17:41.168 --> 17:44.368
ظآزWill be romantic in your eyesظآز

17:44.976 --> 17:46.544
ظآزI came aloneظآز

17:47.408 --> 17:49.232
ظآزBut with you, all is worthwhileظآز

17:49.776 --> 17:53.968
ظآزWe've found a place to belongظآز

17:55.440 --> 17:58.736
ظآزWho hasn't come coated in frostظآز

18:00.208 --> 18:03.568
ظآزBut that won't stop us
from filling our home with sunlightظآز

18:04.016 --> 18:06.032
ظآزThrough heat and coldظآز

18:06.416 --> 18:10.640
ظآزNo one disturbs our peaceظآز

18:11.408 --> 18:15.152
ظآزOur shadows have overlappedظآز

18:18.832 --> 18:22.064
ظآزIn the vast world,
longing only for some moonlightظآز

18:22.064 --> 18:24.432
ظآزSeeking an ordinary lifeظآز

18:24.432 --> 18:27.184
ظآزTo be together side by sideظآز

18:27.184 --> 18:32.144
ظآزYou tugged at my heartstringsظآز

18:32.560 --> 18:34.800
ظآزOur wonderful times are filledظآز

18:34.896 --> 18:37.840
ظآزWith poetic chaptersظآز

18:37.840 --> 18:41.008
ظآزFrom all the world,
we share a cup of teaظآز

18:41.168 --> 18:43.344
ظآزSmall as the fragrance of a flowerظآز

18:43.472 --> 18:45.936
ظآزTo share it with youظآز

18:46.192 --> 18:51.152
ظآزThe candlelight is flickered
by the windظآز

18:52.432 --> 18:56.112
ظآزIn spite of the stormظآز

19:12.336 --> 19:15.568
ظآزNo matter how small a placeظآز

19:15.568 --> 19:18.064
ظآزBy each other's faint lightظآز

19:18.064 --> 19:20.560
ظآزThe rest of our life is clearظآز

19:20.624 --> 19:25.712
ظآزWe're wearing simple robesظآز

19:25.936 --> 19:28.112
ظآزWith your lingering fragranceظآز

19:28.460 --> 19:29.540
Sleep now.

19:31.312 --> 19:34.416
ظآزA river of longing reflects in my gazeظآز

19:34.608 --> 19:37.008
ظآزLet all worries rest deep insideظآز

19:37.008 --> 19:39.536
ظآزNo need to drift againظآز

19:39.536 --> 19:45.072
ظآزThings change, but you're with meظآز

19:45.840 --> 19:50.288
ظآزThe world remains peacefulظآز

19:57.740 --> 19:58.540
What's wrong?

19:59.220 --> 20:00.101
What's with you?

20:00.941 --> 20:02.141
You've been acting strange.

20:03.181 --> 20:04.260
How so?

20:05.381 --> 20:06.780
You're suddenly so attentive to me.

20:09.220 --> 20:10.661
Was I ever unkind to you?

20:17.341 --> 20:18.181
Li.

20:19.300 --> 20:22.381
Do you still feel lonely
living in the mansion now?

20:23.700 --> 20:26.224
No. Plenty of people
in the mansion, after all.

20:26.544 --> 20:27.901
Why, Your Highness?

20:29.220 --> 20:30.421
You'll never feel lonely?

20:31.460 --> 20:32.260
Yes.

20:34.381 --> 20:35.500
And in the Lishan Academy?

20:36.661 --> 20:37.460
Lishan Academy?

20:39.020 --> 20:40.341
So many people there.

20:40.500 --> 20:43.581
Once I wake up,
I'll spend hours just on meals,

20:43.941 --> 20:45.821
leaving scarce time for rest.

20:45.861 --> 20:46.941
No time for loneliness.

20:53.260 --> 20:54.341
What are you doing?

20:56.500 --> 20:57.500
What's this?

21:03.220 --> 21:06.101
Your Highness,
did you eat anything unusual today?

21:07.220 --> 21:08.780
Just as usual.

21:09.500 --> 21:10.980
Speaking of which,

21:11.460 --> 21:13.181
I tried Mumantou this afternoon.

21:13.621 --> 21:15.780
I found it novel and ate quite a bit.

21:18.300 --> 21:21.500
Any past reactions to it, Your Highness?

21:22.460 --> 21:23.780
Never had it before.

21:27.460 --> 21:31.020
Please don't worry, Your Highness.

21:31.181 --> 21:34.621
In my view, Her Highness suffers
from food intolerance.

21:35.300 --> 21:38.581
The rash now is likely harmless.

21:38.901 --> 21:40.101
How to treat it, then?

21:41.381 --> 21:44.260
Stop consumption, Your Highness.

21:44.581 --> 21:46.992
Don't scratch. Drink lots of water.

21:47.472 --> 21:48.821
Recovery should take days.

21:50.101 --> 21:50.901
Thank you.

21:55.056 --> 21:57.901
(Wen Quan)

21:57.901 --> 22:00.020
The petals are added, Your Highness.

22:00.381 --> 22:02.941
Qingyu, why is the water so hot?

22:03.141 --> 22:05.500
Not hot. I just felt it.

22:05.540 --> 22:06.980
Definitely hot. Feel it again.

22:07.300 --> 22:09.700
It's strange.

22:09.901 --> 22:11.060
How could it be hot?

22:13.540 --> 22:14.581
Fell for it, didn't you?

22:14.581 --> 22:16.381
My dress got wet.

22:16.661 --> 22:17.780
Stop it, Your Highness.

22:17.780 --> 22:19.060
Come on, join my bath.

22:19.060 --> 22:20.560
No! I won't!

22:20.592 --> 22:24.848
(Tranquil)

22:26.181 --> 22:27.020
You can't scratch.

22:27.181 --> 22:28.941
The physician warned against it.

22:28.941 --> 22:30.181
Scratching causes scarring.

22:30.901 --> 22:32.101
But it's itchy.

22:32.220 --> 22:33.341
Qingyu is right.

22:33.901 --> 22:36.260
Scratching leads to a disfigured face.

22:37.941 --> 22:39.260
It's not that serious.

22:39.780 --> 22:41.780
It's just a tiny rash.

22:41.941 --> 22:43.661
You're making such a big fuss about it.

22:44.220 --> 22:45.260
Are you a physician?

22:46.901 --> 22:47.780
Yes, I am.

22:47.780 --> 22:50.421
(Wen Quan)
Come, bask in the sun with me.

22:51.341 --> 22:52.141
Alright.

22:59.060 --> 23:01.980
Mark my words, don't scratch.

23:02.821 --> 23:04.901
Bear with it for now.
It will get better tomorrow.

23:07.500 --> 23:10.260
Don't worry.
Qingshuang will stay with me.

23:12.381 --> 23:13.141
Qingshuang?

23:15.141 --> 23:16.700
Qingshuang will stay with me tonight.

23:23.421 --> 23:24.381
I'm sorry?

23:24.821 --> 23:27.381
I'm staying.
We won't sleep in separate rooms.

23:28.740 --> 23:31.621
Are you serious?

23:36.581 --> 23:37.381
Yes.

23:38.500 --> 23:39.300
Li.

23:40.700 --> 23:42.980
We've been married for some time now.

23:44.141 --> 23:45.780
Before, I was disabled,

23:46.581 --> 23:47.861
and I didn't know how you felt.

23:48.381 --> 23:51.941
But now, those concerns are gone.

23:54.500 --> 23:55.780
Time to consummate our marriage.

23:59.141 --> 24:00.020
Why?

24:01.500 --> 24:02.621
What do you mean?

24:04.060 --> 24:05.621
Now that we're husband and wife,

24:05.941 --> 24:08.941
it's natural to share the same bed,
isn't it?

24:09.980 --> 24:11.780
But it never happened before.

24:13.220 --> 24:14.861
Didn't I just explain why?

24:15.861 --> 24:17.460
Before, I was disabled,

24:17.621 --> 24:20.220
and I didn't know how you felt about me.

24:23.141 --> 24:25.861
What? Are you unwilling?

24:28.060 --> 24:29.581
It's not like that.

24:29.980 --> 24:32.944
In that case, let's go to sleep then.

25:05.901 --> 25:07.060
He's fallen asleep?

25:16.621 --> 25:19.780
Stop scratching it. It's almost healed.

25:22.101 --> 25:23.621
You are unwell today.

25:24.220 --> 25:26.780
Relax. Go to bed.

25:29.381 --> 25:30.181
Come on.

25:34.260 --> 25:35.621
I was about to go to bed,

25:35.621 --> 25:38.060
but I was afraid of waking you up.

25:40.101 --> 25:41.141
Why are you laughing?

25:44.141 --> 25:46.621
Li, were you happy today?

25:48.460 --> 25:49.300
Sure.

25:55.581 --> 25:56.901
I hope that from now on,

25:57.220 --> 26:00.581
you'll always be happy like today.

26:01.861 --> 26:04.101
I will, just like today,

26:04.661 --> 26:05.980
stay with you.

26:07.581 --> 26:08.581
The past is in the past.

26:09.381 --> 26:10.661
Late loved ones can't come back.

26:11.821 --> 26:12.941
But we

26:13.941 --> 26:15.220
have to move on.

26:17.141 --> 26:19.980
Li, you lost your mother,

26:20.780 --> 26:22.101
and I lost my father and brother.

26:22.780 --> 26:26.220
From now on, we'll have each other.

26:28.020 --> 26:30.460
No matter what path you take,

26:31.220 --> 26:33.780
smooth or thorny,

26:35.260 --> 26:36.460
I'll be with you.

26:39.141 --> 26:41.101
You won't be alone anymore.

26:44.661 --> 26:45.780
Stop talking.

26:47.460 --> 26:50.621
Once I'm better,
I want to hear it again.

26:53.621 --> 26:54.421
Go to sleep.

27:22.060 --> 27:25.101
Revenue Clerk Gu has arrested my people

27:25.101 --> 27:26.861
without even a heads-up.

27:27.540 --> 27:30.421
If there isn't a good explanation
for this,

27:31.101 --> 27:34.260
don't blame me for losing my cool.

27:34.861 --> 27:36.621
Military Secretary Wang, calm down!

27:37.381 --> 27:40.020
Revenue Clerk Gu knows what he is doing.

27:41.381 --> 27:42.544
But

27:43.780 --> 27:45.780
if he privately detains an officer

27:46.020 --> 27:47.460
without evidence,

27:49.540 --> 27:52.621
I'll absolutely ask the Prefect
for an explanation

27:53.181 --> 27:54.661
and make it clear to all

27:55.020 --> 27:57.776
that the laws are no joke!

27:58.416 --> 27:59.984
Military Secretary Wang, calm down.

28:00.621 --> 28:02.220
Deputy Prefect Zheng,

28:02.341 --> 28:05.780
the arrest was ordered
by the Prefect himself.

28:06.141 --> 28:07.980
As for the reason,

28:10.740 --> 28:13.540
Qiu Xian, a squad leader,

28:13.780 --> 28:15.861
makes 20 guan a year.

28:15.861 --> 28:18.460
According to the Bureau of Revenue,

28:18.460 --> 28:20.540
he has no inherited property
for three generations,

28:20.540 --> 28:22.736
and it's recorded that way

28:22.736 --> 28:24.780
on Wannian County's household register.

28:24.861 --> 28:27.341
Also, the Bureau checked
his three years of spending records.

28:27.341 --> 28:29.101
No large deposits whatsoever.

28:29.101 --> 28:31.020
His income is small.

28:31.020 --> 28:32.784
He has no inheritance or work.

28:32.784 --> 28:36.341
So, how did he
afford the three-courtyard mansion

28:36.341 --> 28:37.621
in Anye Ward a year ago?

28:37.621 --> 28:39.381
The Prefect noticed
his suspicious activity.

28:39.381 --> 28:43.381
So he ordered Bureau of Revenue
and Bureau of Justice to investigate.

28:45.460 --> 28:47.821
I followed the trail,

28:48.020 --> 28:51.101
tracing back to the chase
for the Red Fox in Penglai Alley.

28:51.101 --> 28:55.056
And sure enough,
he vanished midway for almost an hour.

28:55.980 --> 28:58.861
He didn't return
until the target disappeared.

28:58.861 --> 29:02.220
Several of his squad mates testified
and signed statements,

29:02.220 --> 29:05.232
and we have the camp logbook
and patrol maps from that night

29:05.381 --> 29:06.821
as evidence.

29:07.740 --> 29:11.341
Military Secretary Wang,
isn't it already enough to convince you?

29:12.780 --> 29:14.060
Am I allowed to hold him?

29:21.941 --> 29:25.381
Qiu Xian, be honest.

29:26.460 --> 29:27.901
Any false statements?

29:29.101 --> 29:31.821
Speak! What really happened?

29:32.101 --> 29:33.808
How dare you!

29:37.421 --> 29:40.381
Speak! Where did the money come from?

29:40.381 --> 29:42.256
Who did you meet that night?

29:43.621 --> 29:45.381
If you conceal the truth again,

29:45.780 --> 29:48.220
nobody will save your worthless life.

29:51.600 --> 29:53.488
(Meng's Incense Shop)

30:00.464 --> 30:04.912
(Incense)

30:10.941 --> 30:12.381
By the order of Jingzhao Prefecture,

30:12.581 --> 30:14.540
resisters will be killed without mercy!

30:15.540 --> 30:18.821
Sir, spare me, please!

30:18.901 --> 30:20.821
I'm just an incense seller.

30:20.821 --> 30:23.220
Behave yourself.
Answer whatever you're asked,

30:23.341 --> 30:25.181
and you'll spare yourself the pain.

30:25.220 --> 30:27.500
I really am just an incense seller.

30:27.500 --> 30:28.381
Enough!

30:28.621 --> 30:31.540
Speak! Who ordered you?

30:31.540 --> 30:34.740
Who did you contact? Hand over the list!

30:40.141 --> 30:43.381
Okay! Show mercy, please.

30:44.020 --> 30:47.101
I'll get the list for you now.

31:18.901 --> 31:21.181
Your Highness,
urgent notice from Jingzhao Prefecture.

31:38.381 --> 31:39.181
Your Highness.

31:45.421 --> 31:46.220
Over here.

31:51.300 --> 31:53.700
(Tuisi Pavilion)
The traitor is my subordinate Qiu Xian.

31:54.901 --> 31:56.621
On the day we tried to catch Red Fox,

31:56.861 --> 32:00.260
he went to an incense shop
in West Market to warn them.

32:00.260 --> 32:02.141
We rushed over and captured the steward.

32:02.661 --> 32:06.300
But before we interrogated him,
that steward took his own life.

32:08.220 --> 32:09.101
One more thing.

32:09.341 --> 32:12.260
According to the Revenue Clerk,
he used to work in the Eastern Palace.

32:13.740 --> 32:14.540
The Eastern Palace?

32:16.700 --> 32:17.980
Revenue Clerk Gu looked into it.

32:18.141 --> 32:19.381
His name is Chen Bing.

32:19.621 --> 32:22.181
He was a registrar
of the Catering Bureau.

32:22.700 --> 32:25.941
After the fire at the Eastern Palace
eight years ago, he was exiled.

32:26.181 --> 32:29.101
It was previously heard
that he died midway.

32:29.341 --> 32:32.336
He should have died years ago.

32:32.336 --> 32:35.181
Yet he hid in the capital,
selling incense for eight years.

32:37.941 --> 32:41.421
So Yuan Fang's death seems connected
to the Eastern Palace.

32:42.141 --> 32:45.141
Was Deputy Prefect Zheng also present
at the incense shop?

32:45.460 --> 32:46.260
Yes.

32:48.421 --> 32:49.821
Ten years ago,

32:51.020 --> 32:54.621
he served as Director of Rituals
in the Ministry of Rites

32:55.020 --> 32:56.861
and often dealt with the Eastern Palace.

32:57.700 --> 32:58.901
With his eye for detail,

33:00.220 --> 33:02.300
there's no way
he wouldn't recognize Chen Bing.

33:02.941 --> 33:05.101
Deputy Prefect Zheng is suspicious.

33:05.101 --> 33:06.300
Find out what he did tonight.

33:06.300 --> 33:06.901
Yes.

33:08.581 --> 33:09.621
Go to Prince Li's mansion.

33:11.460 --> 33:13.661
Chen Bing killed himself on the spot.

33:13.941 --> 33:15.901
That's what happened.

33:17.141 --> 33:19.220
So Mo Jingli killed Yuan Fang,

33:19.568 --> 33:21.904
trying to sow discord
between the Empress Dowager and me.

33:22.780 --> 33:24.621
The Emperor seizes the chance
to grab power

33:24.980 --> 33:26.421
when we fight.

33:27.260 --> 33:28.500
What does Mo Jingli want?

33:29.381 --> 33:32.101
Zhao Ting! Mobilize my guards,

33:32.421 --> 33:33.381
to Prince Li's mansion.

33:33.381 --> 33:34.141
Yes!

33:53.008 --> 33:53.700
(Jingsi Palace)

33:53.700 --> 33:56.101
(Your Highness,
live first, no matter what.)

33:56.341 --> 33:57.540
(The Crown Prince died.)

33:57.821 --> 34:00.688
(Marquis Muyang and the Empress Dowager
sent men to set the fire.)

34:00.780 --> 34:03.581
(Live on with hatred.)

34:16.701 --> 34:18.660
Hurry! Move everything out. Hurry!

34:20.500 --> 34:21.140
Your Highness.

34:21.620 --> 34:22.500
Let go of me!

34:22.500 --> 34:23.460
Let go!

34:23.460 --> 34:23.980
Let go of me!

34:23.980 --> 34:24.540
Let go!

34:24.540 --> 34:25.221
Your Highness!

34:25.781 --> 34:27.980
Your Highness! What's happening?

34:28.301 --> 34:29.660
Why is it in such chaos?

34:30.540 --> 34:31.861
Tell me, Your Highness!

34:33.341 --> 34:34.221
Chief Secretary Sui.

34:34.861 --> 34:37.620
Did I not order you
to escort her back to Ye Mansion?

34:37.701 --> 34:39.381
Your Highness, I had people...

34:39.381 --> 34:40.221
I won't go back.

34:41.060 --> 34:42.901
Your Highness. I won't leave.

34:43.180 --> 34:44.460
I want to stay with you.

34:45.060 --> 34:46.980
Tell me, what is really happening?

34:46.980 --> 34:48.460
We can face it together.

34:50.540 --> 34:51.861
I apologize to you.

34:52.980 --> 34:54.701
Listen to me. Go.

34:55.701 --> 34:56.781
If I'm lucky enough,

34:57.421 --> 35:00.020
we might meet again.

35:00.301 --> 35:02.020
Your Highness, I won't leave!

35:04.180 --> 35:05.460
Was it that night?

35:05.460 --> 35:06.500
Send her away.

35:07.781 --> 35:08.781
Let go of me!

35:08.781 --> 35:09.301
Let go!

35:09.301 --> 35:10.100
Let go!

35:10.100 --> 35:10.660
Your Highness!

35:10.660 --> 35:11.460
Let go!

35:11.460 --> 35:12.060
Let go!

35:12.060 --> 35:13.460
I'm not leaving, Your Highness!

35:13.980 --> 35:15.221
Let go!

35:17.100 --> 35:18.100
- Ma'am.
- Get out of here.

35:18.100 --> 35:19.381
No, ma'am.

35:19.500 --> 35:20.180
Be good.

35:20.180 --> 35:21.060
- Ma'am.
- Come on.

35:21.060 --> 35:21.821
I won't leave!

35:23.312 --> 35:25.381
Your Highness,
please listen to His Highness.

35:25.381 --> 35:27.421
Going to Ye Mansion now is the safest.

35:27.421 --> 35:29.781
No. His Highness is definitely
hiding something from me.

35:29.861 --> 35:31.221
Something must have happened.

35:31.221 --> 35:32.100
I can't leave, ma'am.

35:32.100 --> 35:32.980
I must stay.

35:32.980 --> 35:34.620
Your Highness, you must leave now.

35:35.020 --> 35:36.020
Yes, Your Highness.

35:37.776 --> 35:39.060
Fire!

35:39.060 --> 35:40.180
Fire!

35:40.741 --> 35:42.660
Fire in His Highness's room!

35:43.100 --> 35:44.100
Your Highness!

35:50.901 --> 35:52.580
- Your Highness
- Your Highness!

35:52.580 --> 35:53.540
No! There's fire!

35:53.540 --> 35:54.901
His Highness is still inside!

35:55.060 --> 35:56.100
Your Highness!

35:56.100 --> 35:56.781
Don't go!

35:56.781 --> 35:57.580
Let me go!

35:57.580 --> 35:58.741
- Get away!
- Your Highness!

35:58.741 --> 35:59.660
- Your Highness!
- Your Highness!

35:59.660 --> 36:00.500
Your Highness!

36:00.500 --> 36:01.781
The fire is too big.

36:01.781 --> 36:02.741
His Highness is inside!

36:02.741 --> 36:03.901
- Get out of here.
- Let me in!

36:03.901 --> 36:05.261
- No!
- Let go of me.

36:05.500 --> 36:06.701
It's dangerous, Your Highness!

36:06.701 --> 36:08.421
Your Highness!

36:08.861 --> 36:09.941
- Let go!
- Your Highness!

36:09.941 --> 36:11.100
Ma'am, please save him.

36:11.460 --> 36:12.901
Ma'am, you must save him.

36:14.140 --> 36:15.941
Your Highness!

36:17.341 --> 36:18.660
Your Highness, hold your breath!

36:18.701 --> 36:21.381
- Your Highness.
- Your Highness.

36:30.341 --> 36:33.421
Revenue Clerk Gu,
take men and seal all the exits.

36:33.421 --> 36:34.620
No one in or out.

36:34.701 --> 36:37.020
Yes. Follow me.

36:37.140 --> 36:40.620
Military Secretary Wang,
take men inside and search thoroughly.

36:40.901 --> 36:42.620
Yes. Follow me.

37:03.504 --> 37:06.896
(Prince Li's Mansion)

37:13.301 --> 37:16.180
Marquis Muyang, you're well-informed.

37:16.701 --> 37:19.060
Any rebels destabilizing Dachu

37:19.901 --> 37:20.901
or acting against me

37:21.660 --> 37:23.180
are always unforgivable.

37:25.296 --> 37:30.384
Fire!

37:43.701 --> 37:45.901
What happened? Where is Prince Li?

37:46.620 --> 37:47.421
Find him quickly!

37:47.781 --> 37:48.580
Follow me!

37:48.688 --> 37:49.424
- Yes.
- Yes.

37:50.096 --> 37:50.768
Hurry!

37:51.861 --> 37:53.500
Prefect, according to the servants,

37:53.500 --> 37:56.221
Prince Li took some close aides
and set fire to themselves inside.

37:56.500 --> 37:58.460
Princess Li was overwhelmed and fainted.

38:04.660 --> 38:05.460
Put out the fire!

38:05.980 --> 38:07.701
Question all relevant individuals.

38:07.781 --> 38:10.221
Take the corpses to Jingzhao Prefecture
for verification.

38:10.861 --> 38:12.781
None shall leave without permission.

38:13.100 --> 38:13.861
Yes.

38:14.421 --> 38:17.180
Who would've thought
Prince Li was behind Yuan Fang's murder?

38:17.180 --> 38:19.861
Now that the truth is exposed,
he killed himself out of guilt.

38:20.060 --> 38:21.421
He deserved death.

38:22.100 --> 38:22.861
Marquis Muyang.

38:24.901 --> 38:27.020
Yuan Fang's case involves many parties.

38:27.421 --> 38:30.060
His Majesty has tasked me
with its investigation.

38:30.660 --> 38:33.180
You don't have to interfere.

38:34.301 --> 38:36.460
I'll report to the Emperor
and the Empress Dowager

38:36.980 --> 38:40.500
to catch the remaining survivors
and maintain national stability.

38:47.980 --> 38:50.060
Why did he go out so late at night?

38:50.261 --> 38:51.861
He left in such a hurry.

38:52.580 --> 38:54.100
Your Highness, don't worry.

38:54.301 --> 38:56.500
Maybe His Highness will be back soon.

38:57.060 --> 38:58.660
I've had Xing cook sleepy soup for you.

38:58.660 --> 39:00.100
Please have some, Your Highness.

39:01.381 --> 39:02.180
Your Highness.

39:07.701 --> 39:11.600
Qingyu, I saw the sky turning red.

39:19.341 --> 39:21.301
Your Highness, slow down!

39:23.020 --> 39:23.901
Be careful!

39:24.100 --> 39:24.861
Your Highness.

39:35.620 --> 39:37.460
Isn't that Prince Li's mansion?

39:50.301 --> 39:52.421
Your Highness, what happened?

39:52.781 --> 39:53.901
Why are still up?

39:54.500 --> 39:56.301
I saw flames shooting into the sky.

39:56.381 --> 39:57.660
It was from Prince Li's mansion.

39:58.100 --> 39:59.301
What happened?

39:59.901 --> 40:03.100
Last night at the Zi hour,
Prince Li's house was suddenly on fire.

40:03.620 --> 40:05.660
The fire spread fiercely,
burning out of control.

40:07.381 --> 40:08.272
Prince Li has died.

40:14.060 --> 40:14.861
Impossible!

40:16.421 --> 40:17.941
Mo Jingli cannot be dead!

40:18.261 --> 40:21.301
I don't believe
he has just died like that.

40:21.620 --> 40:22.941
Your Highness, are you mistaken?

40:22.941 --> 40:23.660
Li.

40:25.221 --> 40:27.421
His dead body has been taken
to the Jingzhao Prefecture.

40:30.416 --> 40:31.824
(Jingzhao Prefecture)

40:31.824 --> 40:33.200
Based on stature

40:33.200 --> 40:36.821
and the remnants
of clothing and accessories,

40:37.020 --> 40:38.941
the four corpses belong to

40:39.140 --> 40:42.421
Prince Li, Chief Secretary Suixin,
Eunuch Jiang Qingbao,

40:42.421 --> 40:44.341
and one of the guards on duty.

40:44.500 --> 40:48.620
Their faces are badly disfigured.

40:51.140 --> 40:52.140
Greetings, Prefect.

40:52.701 --> 40:54.901
This is the physician in service
at Prince Li's mansion.

40:54.941 --> 40:57.500
He attended to Prince Li's health
and knew his appearance well.

40:57.500 --> 40:59.020
He has finished examining the body.

41:03.421 --> 41:05.460
His Highness had an old scar
on his body.

41:05.500 --> 41:07.901
Though this body
was burnt beyond recognition,

41:08.020 --> 41:09.701
most traces suggest a match.

41:10.741 --> 41:12.060
Any other distinctive features?

41:13.500 --> 41:16.261
I once treated His Highness's teeth.

41:16.620 --> 41:18.261
I extracted his left back molar

41:18.341 --> 41:20.901
for him earlier this year.

41:21.341 --> 41:23.821
The left back molar is missing
from this corpse.

41:24.020 --> 41:25.020
It's him indeed.

41:30.096 --> 41:33.552
(Mo Jingli)

41:45.808 --> 41:49.221
Who'd have thought Prince Li intended
to rebel behind our backs?

41:49.701 --> 41:50.301
Mother.

41:55.020 --> 41:55.821
Sister.

41:58.060 --> 41:59.460
You've heard the news as well?

41:59.701 --> 42:00.500
Yes.

42:00.980 --> 42:02.941
Prince Ding
is investigating Yuan Fang's case.

42:02.941 --> 42:05.904
When it implicated the Eastern Palace,
Mo Jingli set himself on fire.

42:08.100 --> 42:08.980
What do you think?

42:10.980 --> 42:13.100
Eight years ago,
the Eastern Palace pressed you hard,

42:13.100 --> 42:14.580
attempting to get you killed.

42:15.140 --> 42:18.301
If not for your immense fortune,
there would be no peace today.

42:19.020 --> 42:20.020
You showed benevolence,

42:20.221 --> 42:22.500
leaving their child alive
and titling him as a prince.

42:22.580 --> 42:25.421
Yet Mo Jingli harbored an ill ambition.

42:25.941 --> 42:28.701
He failed to appreciate your grace,
even plotted secretly

42:28.701 --> 42:30.180
and committed such a rebellious act.

42:30.180 --> 42:32.540
Such a source of disaster
must be eradicated completely.

